//                "description": "<p>It‚Äôs been a minute, but I‚Äôm back‚Äîand today‚Äôs episode is the realest I‚Äôve ever recorded. It‚Äôs our wedding anniversary, and while I‚Äôm swimming in love and gratitude, I‚Äôm also wading through grief, family dysfunction, and the kind of emotional complexity Hallmark doesn‚Äôt make cards for.</p><p><br></p><p>I talk candidly about what it feels like to be fully loved for the first time, the ache of navigating a difficult relationship with my mother (especially through her Alzheimer‚Äôs), and how this life I‚Äôm living now‚Äîauthentic, chosen, intentional‚Äîwasn‚Äôt even on my radar 15 years ago.</p><p><br></p><p>If you‚Äôve ever felt stuck between joy and loss, if you‚Äôre still trying to come home to yourself, or if you&#39;re wondering if true acceptance is even real‚Äîthis one‚Äôs for you.</p><p><br></p><p>No script. No filter. Just real talk from your Big Gay Overalls podcast host.</p><p><br></p><p>üéß Listen now, subscribe, and don‚Äôt forget to share with someone who needs to hear this!</p><p><br></p><p><br>üì≤ Follow on socials @biggayoverallspodcast for more stories, insights, and conversations.</p><p><br></p><p>Burn The Script Book</p><p><br></p><p><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com.au/stores/author/B0DPQXV9VV?ingress=0&visitId=ec11fad7-07fb-4c9f-9086-4e5b4baf9ad2&ref_=ap_rdr\">https://www.amazon.com.au/stores/author/B0DPQXV9VV?ingress=0&amp;visitId=ec11fad7-07fb-4c9f-9086-4e5b4baf9ad2&amp;ref_=ap_rd</a></p><p><br>If you‚Äôd like to connect with me, collaborate, or explore ways we can work together‚Äîwhether it‚Äôs for coaching, storytelling projects, or speaking engagements‚ÄîI‚Äôd love to hear from you!¬†</p><p><br></p><p>Visit <a href=\"http://www.biggayoverallspodcast.com/\">www.biggayoverallspodcast.com</a> or email me directly¬† Let‚Äôs create something meaningful together!</p><p><br>Join our supportive community: Embracing My Big Gay Overalls on Facebook</p><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/share/g/1B